.spectrum-CircleLoader {

  height: 32px;
  position: relative;
  direction: ltr;

  height: 32px;

  border-width: 3px;
  border-radius: 32px;
}
.spectrum-CircleLoader-fills {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}
.spectrum-CircleLoader-fill {

          box-sizing: border-box;
  width: 32px;
